<h2 id="page-heading">Routes Home Page</h2>

<p>This page contains a list of all of your routes. This list contains
several different links. If you would like to view a route on the provided map,
select "map". Selecting "full page" will take you to a specific route's detail
page.</p>

<p>The column heading are active links that can be clicked to sort the list.
The routes list will update automatically once the sorting process is
started. Sorting can be completed on Date, Route Name, and Distance.</p>